										"paragraphStyle" : {
											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "This page covers the default onboarding path: external prerequisites (`python` and `pipenv`), starting the global {{gtClass:PBApplication}} instance, and verifying that the bridge is healthy through inspector details or Python snippets. Read this first when setting up PythonBridge on a new machine, and only jump to troubleshooting if startup or installation fails."
									}
								]
