											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "This page is the operations/debugging reference for startup problems. It explains how to diagnose missing or broken `pipenv`, where the runtime directory lives, how to inspect installation logs, how to manually run the same startup command GT would use, and how to fully reset the runtime environment when you need a clean reinstall."
