										"paragraphStyle" : {
											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "This page shows how to create and manage multiple bridge instances instead of relying on {{gtMethod:PBApplication class>>#uniqueInstance}}. It covers independent ports, starting and stopping ad hoc instances, using them through the same command APIs, and optionally adopting one as the global instance so Python snippets target it."
