											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "This page explains how to run a bridge from a non-default working directory. The key idea is to create a fresh {{gtClass:PBApplication}}, change its `settings workingDirectory:` before startup, install there, and optionally adopt it as the unique instance so Python snippets and source-file workflows use that alternate runtime location."
