											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "This page documents a manual-process mode in which GT connects to a PythonBridge process that you started yourself. It shows how to switch the platform to manual process control, obtain the exact startup command and ports, start/stop the GT side independently of the Python side, explicitly send `quit`, and then reset the platform back to normal."
