											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "This page extends the manual-process story to remote hosts. It explains the security implications of exposing `gtoolkit_bridge` over the network, how to start a remote bridge with `--bind-any-interface`, how to configure a local {{gtClass:PBApplication}} to connect to a remote socket address, what still works through Python snippets after adopting that instance, and which features remain unavailable because the Python executable is remote."
