										"string" : "This page is a user-oriented example of adding contextual inspector views for pandas DataFrame and Series objects. It shows where the supporting Python file lives, how to load it into the running bridge, how to ensure `pandas` is installed, and how to test the result on a sample CSV. Read this when you specifically want richer pandas inspection; use the linked internals page only if you need to modify or extend the implementation."
